short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Send call commands from tel: links to your Snom phone.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Select telephone numbers from websites and pass them over to your Snom-phone's web interface to initiate a call automatically.

This extension supports multiple ways to initiate a call:
- right click on "tel:"-links and choose "Snom Dialer CALL"
- select numbers on websites (then right clicking) 
- click on the extension icon to manually dial a number
